---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="NAMENLOS TATTOO • PAIN • CHAOS • ANARCHY">

  <style>
    .portfolio-img { transition: 0.3s ease; }
    .portfolio-img:hover {
      border-color: #facc15 !important;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
  </style>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center pt-28 relative overflow-hidden">

    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-25">
      <source src="/videos/bg.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
      <h1 class="punk-title text-7xl md:text-[10rem] leading-none mb-4">NAMENLOS</h1>
      <p class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-red-500 mb-6">PAIN IS MY INK</p>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <span class="ru">Я выжигаю свободу на коже. Без правил. Без компромиссов.</span>
        <span class="de">Ich brenne Freiheit in die Haut. Keine Regeln. Keine Kompromisse.</span>
      </p>
      <a href="https://t.me/namenlostattoo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="inline-block border-4 border-red-600 hover:bg-red-600 text-2xl font-black px-12 py-5 transition-all">
        <span class="ru">ЗАБИТЬСЯ НА СЕАНС →</span>
        <span class="de">SESSION BUCHEN →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT ME -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 trash-bg border-t-8 border-red-800">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-center mb-16 text-red-500">
        <span class="ru">ABOUT ME</span>
        <span class="de">ÜBER MICH</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <img src="/images/about/master.jpg" class="w-full border-8 border-red-700 mb-6" alt="Namenlos" />
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <img src="/images/about/process1.jpg" class="w-full border-4 border-red-700" alt="" />
            <img src="/images/about/process2.jpg" class="w-full border-4 border-red-700" alt="" />
            <img src="/images/about/process3.jpg" class="w-full border-4 border-red-700" alt="" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8 text-xl md:text-2xl">
          <p>
            <span class="ru">Я колю там, где другие боятся — на кинк-вечеринках, в подвалах и на рейвах под тяжёлый бас.</span>
            <span class="de">Ich steche dort, wo andere Angst haben — auf Kink-Partys, in Kellern und auf Raves unter schwerem Bass.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="italic">
            <span class="ru">"Если тебе нужна красивая картинка — иди к другим. Ко мне приходят те, кто хочет чувствовать боль и свободу."</span>
            <span class="de">"Wenn du ein schönes Bild willst — geh woanders. Zu mir kommen die, die Schmerz und Freiheit spüren wollen."</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="ru">Без стерильных студий. Только честная кровь, цепи и булавки.</span>
            <span class="de">Keine sterilen Studios. Nur echtes Blut, Ketten und Nadeln.</span>
          </p>
          <div class="text-5xl font-black border-l-8 border-yellow-400 pl-8">
            NO GODS<br />
            NO MASTERS<br />
            ONLY CHAOS
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PORTFOLIO -->
  <section id="portfolio" class="py-20 md:py-28 border-t-8 border-red-800">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-center mb-16 text-red-500">PORTFOLIO</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/chest1.jpg"   class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/chest2.jpg"   class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/chest3.jpg"   class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/skull.jpg"    class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/bird.jpg"     class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/shoulder.jpg" class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/hand.jpg"     class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/leg.jpg"      class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/ear.jpg"      class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/triangle.jpg" class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/text.jpg"     class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
        <img src="/images/portfolio/back.jpg"     class="portfolio-img w-full border-8 border-red-800" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- МОИ ПРОЕКТЫ -->
  <section id="projects" class="py-20 md:py-28 border-t-8 border-red-800 bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-center mb-16 text-red-500">
        <span class="ru">МОИ ПРОЕКТЫ, ГДЕ Я БЬЮ</span>
        <span class="de">MEINE PROJEKTE</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="trash-bg p-10">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">DARK KINK SESSIONS</h3>
          <p class="text-xl">
            <span class="ru">Живые тату-сессии на кинк-вечеринках под красный свет и тяжёлый бас.</span>
            <span class="de">Live-Tattoo-Sessions auf Kink-Partys unter rotem Licht und schwerem Bass.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="trash-bg p-10">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">BASEMENT RAVE TATTOO</h3>
          <p class="text-xl">
            <span class="ru">Мобильная тату-станция в сквотах и подвалах до самого утра.</span>
            <span class="de">Mobile Tattoo-Station in Squats und Kellern bis in den frühen Morgen.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="trash-bg p-10">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">FETISH FLASH NIGHT</h3>
          <p class="text-xl">
            <span class="ru">Специальные флеш-дизайны для BDSM-сессий и fetish-вечеринок.</span>
            <span class="de">Spezielle Flash-Designs für BDSM-Sessions und Fetisch-Partys.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="trash-bg p-10">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">AFTERPARTY CHAOS</h3>
          <p class="text-xl">
            <span class="ru">Тату после основных вечеринок, когда все уже на грани.</span>
            <span class="de">Tattoos nach den Hauptpartys, wenn alle schon am Limit sind.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ЗАПИСАТЬСЯ НА СЕАНС -->
  <section id="booking" class="py-24 md:py-32 border-t-8 border-red-800 bg-red-800 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-8">
        <span class="ru">ЗАПИСАТЬСЯ НА СЕАНС</span>
        <span class="de">SESSION BUCHEN</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-12">
        <span class="ru">Не ищи лёгких путей.<br />Если готов к настоящей метке — пиши.</span>
        <span class="de">Suche nicht den einfachen Weg.<br />Wenn du bereit bist — schreib.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
        <a href="https://t.me/namenlostattoo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 border-8 border-black bg-white text-black text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black py-8 px-16 hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-all">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i> TELEGRAM →
        </a>
        <a href="https://ig.me/m/namenlos_tattoo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 border-8 border-black bg-transparent text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black py-8 px-16 hover:bg-black transition-all">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i> DIRECT →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
